import { Container, Grid, Typography } from "@mui/material"









export const Future=()=>{
    return
    (
        <>
        <Container maxWidth={'lg'}>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item>
                    <Typography variant="h3">
The Future is Now and You Just Need To Realize It. Step into Future Today & Make it Happen.
                    </Typography>

                </Grid>


            </Grid>


        </Container>
        </>
    )
}
